item.title: Wonder Woman Historia
item.description: body { background-image: url('/img/fiction/wonder-woman-historia-2023.avif'); } Wonder Woman Historia: The Amazons. Kelly Sue DeConnick; Phil Jimenez; Gene Ha; Nicola Scott. www.dc.com . wonder-woman.fandom.com . www.hoopladigital.com . Accessed Oct 5, 2024. The subjugations and abuses of not-men by men are too numerous to catalog in a library… let alone a book. “It’s just his nature,” they say. We say nature may be brutal, but it is not sinister.
